{{Contains Khmer text}}

'''白馬省'''（{{lang-km|ខេត្តកែប}}，{{IPA-km|kʰaet kaep}}），簡稱'''白馬'''（{{lang-km|កែប}}），是柬埔寨最小的{{link-en|柬埔寨省份|Provinces of Cambodia|省級政區}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://donboscokep.org/kep-national-park |title=Kep National Park |publisher=donboscokep.org |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120501181654/http://donboscokep.org/kep-national-park |archivedate=2012-05-01 }}</ref>，面積336平方公里，人口40280人。<ref name="Statistics"/>該省的高棉語名字意思是“馬鞍”。

白馬省位於柬埔寨南部，靠近[[越南|越南]]，面臨[[泰國灣|泰國灣]]。原屬[[貢布省|貢布省]]。1993年，白馬升格為直轄市。2008年12月22日，根據皇家法令，白馬市與[[丹那章厄县|丹那章厄县]]一起自貢布省析出，與[[拜林省|拜林]]、[[西哈努克省|西哈努克]]同時升格為的省級行政區。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://khmerization.blogspot.com/2008/12/decree-creates-three-new-provinces.html |title=Decree creates three new provinces |date=December 2008 |publisher=khmerization.blogspot.com |access-date=2016-10-15 |archive-date=2012-08-09 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69n6SLd1b?url=http://khmerization.blogspot.com/2008/12/decree-creates-three-new-provinces.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/decree-creates-three-new-provinces |title=Decree creates three new provinces by Vong Sokheng |publisher=The Phnom Penh Post |date=December 31, 2008 |accessdate=December 24, 2015 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927002355/https://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/decree-creates-three-new-provinces |dead-url=no }}</ref>

白馬省首府位於[[白馬市|白馬市]]，該市有一座[[白馬國家公園|白馬國家公園]]，為柬埔寨的旅遊景點。

== 政區 ==
白馬轄領兩個政區：

* [[丹那章厄县|丹那章厄县]]（ស្រុកដំណាក់ចង្អើរ）：是白馬的最大政區，被分為三個子政區。西部的Angkaol，中部的Ou Krasar，以及東部的磅德{{lang-en|Pong Tuek}}。<ref>[http://statsnis.org/areaname/vill_pro23.htm National Institute of Statistics, Kep Province, Damnak Chang'aeur District] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080803013555/http://statsnis.org/areaname/vill_pro23.htm |date=2008-08-03 }}</ref>
* [[白馬市|白馬市]]（ក្រុងកែប）：位於該省的中央位置，區內再分為兩個子政區──位於白馬半島東部的白馬分區（{{lang-en|Sangkat Kep}}）以及西部的波羅丹分區（{{lang-en|Sangkat Prey Thum}}）。<ref>General Population Census of Cambodia 1998, Ministry of Planning, Phnom Penh</ref>

== 地理 ==

===白馬群島===
白馬半島向西南伸入白馬灣，白馬半島的東南方有一群由13座海島組成的迷你群島稱為白馬群島。

# {{link-en|兔島 (柬埔寨)|Koh Tonsay}}
# Kok島
# Matay島
# Svay島 (កោះស្វាយ, 'Mango Island')
# Kbal島 (កោះក្បាល, 'Head Island')
# Hal Trey島(កោះហាលត្រី)
# Svay Prey島 (កោះស្វាយព្រៃ)
# Sarang島(កោះសារ៉ាង)
# Pou島 (កោះពោធិ, 'Enlightening Island')
# Makprang島 (កោះម៉ាកប្រាង)
# Angrong島 (កោះអង្គ្រង, 'Thorny Tree Islet')
# Seh島 (កោះអាចម៍សេះ, 'Horse Island')
# Sngout島 (កោះស្ងួត)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kohrong-sanloem.com/geography/list-of-islands|title=List of Islands|publisher=Cambodia islands – Island Species Cambodia|date=|accessdate=May 16, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150516191541/http://kohrong-sanloem.com/geography/list-of-islands|archivedate=2015年5月16日}}</ref>

====兔島====
[[File:Koh_Tonsay_2.jpg|thumb]]
{{main|兔島 (柬埔寨)}}
兔島（{{lang-km|កោះទន្សាយ}}）位於白馬市的西南方約4.5公里。兔島海岸的沙灘是吸引觀光客的賣點，而海底形形色色的珊瑚及海生動植物吸引動物學家及研究者造訪。

兔島之名源於Rumsay。
<!--
Koh Tonsay is 2 square kilometers in area. During then-Prince Norodom Sihanouk’s Sangku Reastr Niyum regime, it was used as a place to rehabilitate criminals, who were also used to defend the island. Horse cart paths and wooden, thatch roofed motels were also constructed during this time. Most of this infrastructure has been destroyed by weather and decades of war. 
Today Koh Tonsay is a major tourist attraction for Kep. There are about 8 khmer run basic guest houses and about 5 restaurants, serving mainly fresh seafood like crabs, shrimps and fish. During the day it can get quite busy with day tourists, which leave around 4pm, so for the sunset there are only a few overnight people there. Electricity runs only from 6-9pm by generators. 
Water can run short during the dry months (Dec-Apr) and longtail boats with big water tanks are supllying the demand.-->

== 歷史 ==
白馬在法屬殖民時期屬於貢布轄區（{{lang-fr|Circonscription Résidentielle de Kampot}}），<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kyoto-seas.org/pdf/42/4/420402.pdf |title=Kampot of the Belle Époque: From the Outlet of Cambodia to a Colonial Resort |website=Center for Southeast Asian Studies, Kyoto |date= |accessdate=December 26, 2015 |archive-date=2017-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809060923/https://kyoto-seas.org/pdf/42/4/420402.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>並發展成為柬埔寨一座頗負盛名的濱海城鎮。白馬1908年設立，名為''Kep-Sur-Mer''，它是法國和柬埔寨的上流人士的渡假勝地，作為渡假地直到1970年代。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.phnompenhpost.com/7days/kep-villas-ghosts-arts-past |title=Kep villas: ghosts of arts past |publisher=The Phnom Penh Post |date=December 28, 2012 |accessdate=December 24, 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101130816/https://www.phnompenhpost.com/7days/kep-villas-ghosts-arts-past |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在法屬殖民期之後的1953年至1970年間建造的白馬現代風格村落，建築師[[旺莫利萬|旺莫利萬]]及{{link-en|盧班漢|Lu Ban Hap}}體現了柬埔寨的現代主義建築的黃金時代，它是一種揉合多種元素的運動，包含高棉傳統建築元素。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://evds.ucalgary.ca/news/alexander-doerr-sudden-death-cambodias-homegrown-modernism |title=ALEXANDER DOERR ON THE SUDDEN DEATH OF CAMBODIA'S HOMEGROWN MODERNISM |publisher=University of Calgary |date= |accessdate=December 26, 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114833/https://evds.ucalgary.ca/news/alexander-doerr-sudden-death-cambodias-homegrown-modernism |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

